---
By: Han Shan
Source:
  ISBN: 1556591403
  Locus:
    Page: 253
  Publisher: Copper Canyon Press
  Title: The Collected Songs of Cold Mountain
  Translator: Red Pine
---
Cold Mountain is so cold
ice locks up the rocks
concealing mountain green
revealing winter white
then the sun shines
and the ice begins to melt
on this warmth
an old man survives
